extracted_text: Sucres. Encore calme et on attend la semaine prochaine; peut-être il y aurait une demande. Les deux dernières semaines passées, détaillé. Sous contrat. J’avis ce soir.
Translation_to_English: Sugars. Still calm and we are waiting for next week; perhaps there will be some demand. The last two weeks gone, detailed. Under contract. I have given notice this evening.
